name: Sebastian Melchior
about: Medical Director in the Urology Clinic at Bremen-Mitte. Specializes in robot-assisted surgery. Listed among best German urologists in 2015 according to Focus edition.

name: Thomas W Kraus
specialization: Surgical oncologist, Gastrointestinal surgeon, Pancreatic surgeon

name: Stefanie Veit
about: Heads the minimally invasive technology division of the German Society of Thoracic Surgery.

name: Ralf Buhl
about: Dr. Ralf Buhl has provided over 4,000 successful neurosurgeries. Among his patients are famous politicians, businessmen, musicians, actors. In 2015, a Hollywood star George Clooney had severe back pain and was treated by Professor Buhl.

name: Sebastian Hentsch
language: Doctor speaks Russian, English, German, French

name: Axel Stang
about: Awarded Innovation in Medicine Asklepios Prize.

name: Michael Friedrich
about: Member of the American Society of Clinical Oncology and the International Gynecologic Cancer Society.

name: Ulrich Schaudig
about: Head of the Ophthalmology Department at Asklepios Barmbek

name: Manuela Seifert
about: Dr. Seifer applies breast conserving operations as a key treatment method.

name: Per-Ulf Tunn
about: Author of several methods of bone tumors treatment, incl. limb perfusion in advanced soft tissue sarcoma.

name: Prof. Dr. Anca-Ligia Grosu
about: Prof. Dr. Anca-Ligia Grosu is a celebrated Radiation Oncologist with more than 25 years of experience.
